on-making with AI agents,\ndelivers a personal healthcare assistant to patients, and continuously learns from doctor feedback вҖ” creating a closed-loop system.", "lineHeight": 1.4, "autoResize": true}, {"id": "pillar_label", "type": "text", "x": 120, "y": 278, "width": 300, "height": 22, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "text": "FOUR CORE PILLARS", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 7, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "FOUR CORE PILLARS", "lineHeight": 1.25, "autoResize": true}, {"id": "p1_box", "type": "rectangle", "x": 120, "y": 308, "width": 248, "height": 100, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#0b7285", "backgroundColor": "#e3fafc", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 10, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "p1_text", "type": "text", "x": 130, "y": 318, "width": 228, "height": 80, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#0b7285", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "text": "1. Global Health\nData Center\nCentralise every patient's\nfull medical history", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 11, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "1. Global Health\nData Center\nCentralise every patient's\nfull medical history", "lineHeight": 1.4,