         multi-select            Optional    Immune suppression context; infection risk escalation\nEndocrine / Hormonal Conditions    multi-select            Optional    Metabolic context; drug metabolism and dosing rules\nPrevious Blood Transfusions        boolean + date          Optional    Transfusion reaction history; blood product safety flags\nOrgan Transplant History           boolean + organ         Optional    Immunosuppressant drug context; rejection risk flags\nDisability / Mobility Limitations  multi-select            Optional    Care pathway adaptation; accessible treatment planning\nVaccination History (key vaccines) multi-select            Optional    Immunisation gap analysis; travel health recommendations\nGenetic / Hereditary Conditions    text                    Optional    Genetic risk overlay on family history correlations\nPrevious Adverse Drug Reactions    text (drug + reaction)  Optional    Distinct from allergies; pharmacovigilance context", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 63, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "Field Name                         Data Type               Required?   AI Pipeline Purpose\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nChronic / Long-term Conditions     multi-select            Required    RAG context window (permanent patient profile)\nPrevious Surgeries                 text (name + date)      Optional    Surgical history for anaesthetic risk, scar tissue context\nPrevious Hospitalisations          text (reason + date)    Optional    Severity history; pat