              вҶ’  Risk stratification model, preventive care engine\nFamily History                     вҶ’  Genetic risk overlay, screening recommendation engine\nPrevious Records (uploads)         вҶ’  OCR extraction вҶ’ RAG ingestion вҶ’ history summariser\nSpeech Consent                     вҶ’  Real-time ASR pipeline (Whisper / Deepgram) вҶ’ conversation analysis вҶ’ ambient note gen\nAll structured fields              вҶ’  Global Health Data Center (versioned, timestamped)\nDoctor corrections (per visit)     вҶ’  Feedback loop вҶ’ model fine-tuning / RLHF pipeline", "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 132, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "Field Category                     вҶ’  AI Pipeline Target\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nDemographics + Blood Group         вҶ’  Emergency alert engine, drug dosing rules\nChronic Conditions + History       вҶ’  RAG context window (permanent patient profile)\nCurrent Symptoms                   вҶ’  Symptom correlation agent, triage scoring\nMedications + Allergies            вҶ’  Drug interaction engine, contraindication suppression\nLifestyle + Habits                 вҶ’  Risk stratification model, preventive care engine\nFamily History                     вҶ’  Genetic risk overlay, screening recommendation engine\nPrevious Records (uploads)         вҶ’  OCR extraction вҶ’ RAG ingestion вҶ’ history summariser\nSpeech Consent                     вҶ’  Real-time ASR pipeline (Whisper / Deepgram) вҶ’ conversation analysis вҶ’ ambient note gen\nAll structured fields              вҶ’  Global Health Data Center (versioned, timestamped)\nDoctor corrections (per visit)     вҶ’  Feedback loop вҶ’ model fine-tuning / RLHF pipeline", "lineHeight": 1.55, "autoResize": true}, {"id": "legend_frame", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 5960, "width": 1100, "height": 140, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "backgroundColor": "#f1f3f5", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "dashed", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 140, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "legend_text", "type": "text", "x": 120, "y": 5972, "width": 1060, "height": 116, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "text": "LEGEND & NOTES\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nCOLLECTED ONCE  =  Fields forming the permanent patient profile in the Global Health Data Center\nвҳ… UPDATED EVERY VISIT  =  Re-collected at each encounter; versioned with visit timestamp\n* Required if allergy present   |   Conditional = required only when a parent field is triggered\nTotal fields across all 10 sections: ~120   |   ESAP Intelligent AI Healthcare Platform  |  2026", "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 141, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "LEGEND & NOTES\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\nCOLLECTED ONCE  =  Fields forming the permanent patient profile in the Global Health Data Center\nвҳ… UPDATED EVERY VISIT  =  Re-collected at each encounter; versioned with visit timestamp\n* Required if allergy present   |   Conditional = required only when a parent field is triggered\nTotal fields across all 10 sections: ~120   |   ESAP Intelligent AI Healthcare Platform  |  2026", "lineHeight": 1.55, "autoResize": true}, {"id": "loop_section_header", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 6130, "width": 1100, "height": 60, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1864ab", "backgroundColor": "#1864ab", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 200, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "loop_section_header_text", "type": "text", "x": 200, "y": 6146, "width": 900, "height": 28, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#ffffff", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "text": "THE CLOSED LOOP  вҖ”  How ESAP Continuously Improves", "fontSize": 18, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 201, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "THE CLOSED LOOP  вҖ”  How ESAP Continuously Improves", "lineHeight": 1.25, "autoResize": true}, {"id": "loop_vision_box", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 6210, "width": 1100, "height": 70, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1864ab", "backgroundColor": "#e7f5ff", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 202, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "loop_vision_text", "type": "text", "x": 120, "y": 6224, "width": 1060, "height": 42, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#1c3a5e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "text": "\"The ambition is a closed loop: patient data feeds the AI  вҶ’  AI helps doctors  вҶ’  doctors correct the AI  вҶ’  corrections improve the AI\"\nвҖ” Build an AI-powered healthcare platform that centralises all patient health data, augments clinical decision-making, delivers a personal assistant, and continuously learns.", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top", "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 203, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "originalText": "\"The ambition is a closed loop: patient data feeds the AI  вҶ’  AI helps doctors  вҶ’  doctors correct the AI  вҶ’  corrections improve the AI\"\nвҖ” Build an AI-powered healthcare platform that centralises all patient health data, augments clinical decision-making, delivers a personal assistant, and continuously learns.", "lineHeight": 1.5, "autoResize": true}, {"id": "loop_outer_frame", "type": "rectangle", "x": 100, "y": 6300, "width": 1100, "height": 820, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#adb5bd", "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "dashed", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 204, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false}, {"id": "ln_patient", "type": "rectangle",